[146.5575, "o", "- **Bucket names must be globally unique** - \"sample-bucket\" is likely already taken. Consider using a unique name like `sample-bucket-<your-username>-<timestamp>`.\r\n- **Public buckets have security implications** - Only make buckets public if you intend to serve public content.\r\n- **Block Public Access settings** - Some AWS accounts have Block Public Access enabled by default, which may prevent making buckets public even with these commands.\r\n"]
